# Description: Master changelog file for the Recrutech authentication service database schema
# 
# This file orchestrates the creation of all database tables and constraints
# in the proper dependency order to ensure referential integrity.
#
# Schema Overview:
# - Core Authentication: Users table with comprehensive security features
# - Company Management: Companies table for business entities
# - HR Management: HR employees table linking users to companies
# - Applicant Management: Applicants table for job seekers
#
# Dependency Order:
# 1. users (base table, no dependencies)
# 2. companies (depends on users for admin_user_id)
# 3. hr_employees (depends on users and companies)
# 4. applicants (depends on users)
-->
